          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is for recitation and contemplation and is a collection (paddhati) of more than 500 poetic verses that cover a range of topics from love, anguish, women, sex, artha, karma, and dharma; additionally contains instructions for morality, gardening, omens, weapons, and other kinds of practical advice. Manuscript is incomplete and lacks an ending, but contains most of the text.</summary>
